body:
A low bandwidth news app where a user can choose his preferences of news. We have a designed three solutions for the same,

1. Web Application: We are planning to create a web application in Python flask that allows the user to create an account and view latest news according to his preferences.

2. A news reader: A text-to-speech generator that can read the news to the user.

3. A text-based news delivery system: News delivered in the form of text message, particularly targeted in users with limited Internet  accessibility.

References:
1. Personalized news recommendation based on click behavior :  http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1719976
2. A contextual-bandit approach to personalized news article recommendation : http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1772758
3. Multilingual Information Retrieval and Smart News Feed Based on Big Data : http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7396613/?reload=true&arnumber=7396613&tag=1
4. Personalized news retrieval system : https://www.google.com/patents/US20050028194 
5. An adaptive personalized news dissemination system : http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10844-008-0053-8
